1. Co' nen khai bao ham` khoi tao la private khong ? 
---> khong nen nha 
	+ Helper/ Utility class
	+ Build Pattern
	
2. Tai sao khai bao' cac' thuoc tinh' trong class la` private thay vi` public ?
---> vi` 
	+ Dam bao quy tac OOP(moi class chi chua' thong tin rieng cua no)/// =>> !FOP : share data
	+ Han che truy cap tu` nhung doi' tuong khong can` thiet' -- VD : Employee <--> Company
																		- Money cua cong ty se giam
																		- Luong nhan vien se tang
																		- Nhung nhan vien & cong ty khong biet tai khoan cua nguoi` con` lai

3. Khai' niem this ? 
	+ Doi tuong current dang call function non-static
	
4. Tu` khoa' static ?
	+ static attribute
	+ static method